{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"keepScreenOn","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration(py)keepScreenOn","title":"keepScreenOn","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"keepScreenOn","kind":"identifier"}]},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"dynamic"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"keepScreenOn"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"set"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"abstract":[{"text":"If enabled the idle timer of the device will be disabled while the scanner is active, preventing the device from going to sleep (dim and lock screen).","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/keepscreenon"]},{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/keepscreenon"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/keepScreenOn"},"references":{"doc://net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration/keepScreenOn":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"keepScreenOn"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/keepScreenOn","abstract":[{"text":"If enabled the idle timer of the device will be disabled while the scanner is active, preventing the device from going to sleep (dim and lock screen).","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/keepscreenon","role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"keepScreenOn","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"keepScreenOn"}]},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK":{"title":"ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Version: 8.0.1"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk","kind":"symbol","role":"collection"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration":{"title":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The energy management configuration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and subclasses sport a customizable energy management system.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Since scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"well as in energy saving mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"video frames per second.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}},"variantOverrides":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"\/identifier\/interfaceLanguage","value":"occ"},{"op":"replace","path":"\/metadata\/roleHeading","value":"Instance Property"},{"op":"replace","path":"\/metadata\/title","value":"keepScreenOn"},{"op":"replace","path":"\/met